<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>哲学とは？</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap');

:root {
–ink: #1a1a2e;
–paper: #f5f0e8;
–accent: #c84b31;
–gold: #d4a843;
–sky: #4a7fa5;
–sage: #5c8a6e;
–line: #1a1a2e22;
}

- { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: var(–paper);
color: var(–ink);
font-family: ‘Zen Kaku Gothic New’, sans-serif;
min-height: 100vh;
padding: 40px 20px 60px;
background-image:
repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 39px, var(–line) 39px, var(–line) 40px);
}

.page {
max-width: 700px;
margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ── Header ── */
.header {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 48px;
animation: fadeDown 0.7s ease both;
}
.header .eyebrow {
font-size: 11px;
letter-spacing: 0.3em;
color: var(–accent);
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.header h1 {
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.15;
letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.header .subtitle {
margin-top: 10px;
font-size: 0.95rem;
color: #555;
}

/* ── Big Question Box ── */
.big-q {
background: var(–ink);
color: var(–paper);
border-radius: 4px;
padding: 28px 32px;
margin-bottom: 36px;
position: relative;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
}
.big-q .label {
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 0.3em;
color: var(–gold);
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.big-q p {
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
font-size: 1.15rem;
line-height: 1.8;
}
.big-q .corner {
position: absolute;
top: 12px; right: 14px;
font-size: 2.2rem;
opacity: 0.18;
}

/* ── Section title ── */
.section-title {
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 0.35em;
color: var(–accent);
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 16px;
margin-top: 40px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
}
.section-title::after {
content: ‘’;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: var(–accent);
opacity: 0.35;
}

/* ── Tree diagram ── */
.tree {
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.25s ease both;
}
.tree-root {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
margin-bottom: 0;
}
.root-node {
background: var(–ink);
color: var(–paper);
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
font-size: 1rem;
font-weight: 700;
padding: 14px 32px;
border-radius: 2px;
letter-spacing: 0.1em;
position: relative;
}
.root-node::after {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
bottom: -24px; left: 50%;
transform: translateX(-50%);
width: 2px; height: 24px;
background: var(–ink);
}

.branches {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-around;
margin-top: 24px;
position: relative;
gap: 8px;
}
.branches::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
top: 0; left: 15%; right: 15%;
height: 2px;
background: var(–ink);
}

.branch {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
flex: 1;
min-width: 0;
}
.branch-line {
width: 2px;
height: 20px;
background: var(–ink);
}
.branch-node {
border: 2px solid var(–ink);
border-radius: 2px;
padding: 10px 12px;
text-align: center;
width: 100%;
font-size: 0.78rem;
line-height: 1.5;
}
.branch-node .en {
font-size: 0.65rem;
opacity: 0.5;
margin-top: 2px;
}
.branch-node.col-1 { border-color: var(–accent); color: var(–accent); }
.branch-node.col-2 { border-color: var(–sky); color: var(–sky); }
.branch-node.col-3 { border-color: var(–sage); color: var(–sage); }
.branch-node.col-4 { border-color: var(–gold); color: var(–gold); }

/* ── 4 Questions grid ── */
.q-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 14px;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
}
.q-card {
border: 1.5px solid var(–ink);
border-radius: 2px;
padding: 18px 16px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
transition: transform 0.2s ease;
}
.q-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
.q-card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
top: 0; left: 0;
width: 4px; height: 100%;
}
.q-card.c1::before { background: var(–accent); }
.q-card.c2::before { background: var(–sky); }
.q-card.c3::before { background: var(–sage); }
.q-card.c4::before { background: var(–gold); }

.q-card .num {
font-size: 0.65rem;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
opacity: 0.4;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.q-card .q-text {
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
font-size: 1rem;
font-weight: 700;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.q-card .q-desc {
font-size: 0.78rem;
line-height: 1.65;
color: #444;
}
.q-card .q-example {
margin-top: 8px;
font-size: 0.72rem;
color: #777;
font-style: italic;
}

/* ── Philosophers row ── */
.phil-row {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
overflow-x: auto;
padding-bottom: 4px;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
}
.phil-row::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 4px; }
.phil-row::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
.phil-row::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(–ink); border-radius: 2px; }

.phil-card {
border: 1.5px solid var(–ink);
border-radius: 2px;
padding: 14px 16px;
min-width: 140px;
flex-shrink: 0;
text-align: center;
}
.phil-card .avatar {
font-size: 1.8rem;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.phil-card .name {
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 0.85rem;
margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.phil-card .period {
font-size: 0.65rem;
opacity: 0.5;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.phil-card .quote {
font-size: 0.72rem;
line-height: 1.6;
color: #555;
font-style: italic;
}

/* ── Summary strip ── */
.summary {
background: var(–ink);
color: var(–paper);
padding: 24px 28px;
border-radius: 2px;
text-align: center;
animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.5s ease both;
}
.summary .tag {
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 0.35em;
color: var(–gold);
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.summary p {
font-family: ‘Noto Serif JP’, serif;
font-size: 1.05rem;
line-height: 1.85;
}

/* ── Animations ── */
@keyframes fadeDown {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-18px); }
to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes fadeUp {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- Header -->

  <div class="header">
    <div class="eyebrow">10歳にもわかる説明 / ELI10</div>
    <h1>哲学とは<br>なにか？</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">「なぜ？」と問いつづけることの学問</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Big Q -->

  <div class="big-q">
    <div class="label">CORE IDEA</div>
    <p>
      哲学とは、<strong>「当たり前」とされていることに<br>
      あえて疑問を持ち、深く考える</strong>営みです。<br>
      答えを出すことより、<em>問い方そのもの</em>を磨く学問。
    </p>
    <div class="corner">？</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tree -->

  <div class="section-title">哲学の構造</div>
  <div class="tree">
    <div class="tree-root">
      <div class="root-node">哲学 (Philosophy)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="branches">
      <div class="branch">
        <div class="branch-line"></div>
        <div class="branch-node col-1">
          形而上学<br>
          <span class="en">Metaphysics</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="branch">
        <div class="branch-line"></div>
        <div class="branch-node col-2">
          認識論<br>
          <span class="en">Epistemology</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="branch">
        <div class="branch-line"></div>
        <div class="branch-node col-3">
          倫理学<br>
          <span class="en">Ethics</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="branch">
        <div class="branch-line"></div>
        <div class="branch-node col-4">
          論理学<br>
          <span class="en">Logic</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4 Questions -->

  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:48px;">4つの根本問題</div>
  <div class="q-grid">
    <div class="q-card c1">
      <div class="num">01 / 形而上学</div>
      <div class="q-text">「存在」とは？</div>
      <div class="q-desc">この世界はどうやって成り立っているか。神はいるか。時間・空間の正体は何か。</div>
      <div class="q-example">例：「夢と現実のちがいは？」</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card c2">
      <div class="num">02 / 認識論</div>
      <div class="q-text">「知る」とは？</div>
      <div class="q-desc">私たちは何を、どこまで知ることができるか。感覚は信頼できるか。</div>
      <div class="q-example">例：「見ていないとき、ものはある？」</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card c3">
      <div class="num">03 / 倫理学</div>
      <div class="q-text">「善」とは？</div>
      <div class="q-desc">何が正しくて、何が悪いか。どう生きるべきか。ルールの根拠はどこにあるか。</div>
      <div class="q-example">例：「嘘をついてもいい場面は？」</div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card c4">
      <div class="num">04 / 論理学</div>
      <div class="q-text">「考える」とは？</div>
      <div class="q-desc">正しい推論の形とは何か。矛盾のない思考はどう作るか。</div>
      <div class="q-example">例：「全員が嘘つきなら誰を信じる？」</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Philosophers -->

  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:40px;">代表的な哲学者</div>
  <div class="phil-row">
    <div class="phil-card">
      <div class="avatar">🏛️</div>
      <div class="name">ソクラテス</div>
      <div class="period">BC 469–399</div>
      <div class="quote">「無知の知」<br>知らないと気づくことが知の始まり</div>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-card">
      <div class="avatar">🌐</div>
      <div class="name">デカルト</div>
      <div class="period">1596–1650</div>
      <div class="quote">「我思う、ゆえに我あり」<br>疑えないものから始める</div>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-card">
      <div class="avatar">⚖️</div>
      <div class="name">カント</div>
      <div class="period">1724–1804</div>
      <div class="quote">「義務」こそ道徳の基礎。結果でなく動機が問われる</div>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-card">
      <div class="avatar">🔨</div>
      <div class="name">ニーチェ</div>
      <div class="period">1844–1900</div>
      <div class="quote">「神は死んだ」<br>自ら価値を創りだせ</div>
    </div>
    <div class="phil-card">
      <div class="avatar">🗣️</div>
      <div class="name">ウィトゲンシュタイン</div>
      <div class="period">1889–1951</div>
      <div class="quote">言語の限界が思考の限界。言葉を疑え</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Summary -->

  <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:40px;">まとめ</div>
  <div class="summary">
    <div class="tag">TAKEAWAY</div>
    <p>
      哲学は「答え」を覚える学問ではありません。<br>
      <strong>「問い」の質を高める</strong>訓練です。<br>
      日常のあらゆる「当たり前」に<em>「本当に？」</em>と問いかけるとき、<br>
      あなたはすでに哲学をしています。
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>